This is a project that lets you write your wifi settings and lets you
generate a QR code for those settings. The displayed QR code can be used
(Barcode Scanner on Android) to set settings in your smartphone. 

Note: 
If you have Git version <1.7.5 please run "git submodule update". 

Usage: 
	./main.py (this will print a help text, or use -h to get help)
	

main.py --ssid=MyNetwork --password=secret123 --auth=WPA

